------------------------------------
ows-php-selenium.xpi:
------------------------------------

This is a selenium ide (firefox plugin) format bundle allowing you to create custom PHP test classes
and methods, it uses the ows-phpunit framework by default. 

* OWS (PHPUnit): Generates test classes extending OWSeleniumTestCase (this is a configurable option).
* OWS (PHPUnit hardcoded url): With this format, test URLs are defined by an environement variable
named "DOMAIN" inside a phpunit .xml configuration file. See the ows_phpunit/conf/example_conf.xml.

source code: git clone -b ows-php-formatter src/content/formats/php-ows-selenium.js

github fork: https://github.com/B2F/PHP-Formatter
original github project: https://github.com/brokenthumbs
------------------------------------
